Version 0.8

* added Spanish translation
* added Slovak translation
* added Brazilian Portuguese translation
* added zooming feature
* added PopUp menu with addition functions "Fit Page", "Fit Width",
  "First Page" and "Last Page"
* added Frensh translation
* disable menu entries when already zoom to the target size of the entry
* add new prefs option to set initial zoom

Version 0.7

* Added gettext support to plugin, so that texts used by the plugin
  can now be translated
  (will only work with Sylpheed-Claws >= 0.9.12cvs3)

Version 0.6

* update for changes in Sylpheed

Version 0.5

* update to use new Sylpheed Plugin build system with installed
  header files and pkg-config

Version 0.4

* Added preferences for antialiasing and respect eof
* make it work with Ghostscript 8

Version 0.3

* First public release
